          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="v7wYzxMNztZIk_eU5v4j-25" parent="1" style="ellipse;shape=cloud;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontColor=#31BAFF;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;External Payment network&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;(Visa, Mastercard etc)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="150" width="265" x="492.5" y="570" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="v7wYzxMNztZIk_eU5v4j-26" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" value="&lt;span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;font-size: 23px;&quot;&gt;Security concerns&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;1. Validating merchants&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;2. Protecting customers personal info&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="460" x="-570" y="1040" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="v7wYzxMNztZIk_eU5v4j-27" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;&quot;&gt;1.Validating merchants&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 23px; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration-line: underline; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Provide two set of keys while merchant onboarding&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;1. Public API key - to be part of Headers like - Bearer &amp;lt;API_KEY&amp;gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;2. Private secret key securely stored in merchants server to authenticate the&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;merchant server with our system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 23px; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;For each request the merchant server generates a digital signature using request details(body, public key, endpoint, parameters) along with timestamp and a unique nonce using secret key, it can never be tampered because the signature contains the timestamp or nonce was already used&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="340" width="790" x="-100" y="820" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="v7wYzxMNztZIk_eU5v4j-29" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;&quot;&gt;2.Protect Customer private info&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Using Iframe and encryption&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;Our server generates and maintain key encryption key-pairs&lt;br&gt;we provide a JavaScript SDK which loads an Iframe from our domain on the merchant webpage and uses the encryption keys to secure the data.&lt;br&gt;When customer enters the card details on the iframe , it encrypts the data and sends it directly to our system using HTTPS , where it gets decrypted using the private key stored in HSM&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="790" x="770" y="820" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="v7wYzxMNztZIk_eU5v4j-30" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;IFrame&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
